deck: Reggie Riot's girlfriend.
description:
Origin

A girl dating Reggie Jones that tries to help him work through some of his issues with his parents.

Creation

Written by Shaun Simon and drawn by Mike Allred.

Major Story Arcs

During a night of drug use, Reggie begins ragging on his mother and Jess tries to rationalize with him. He decides to go out for more drugs and Jess intends to accompany him after telling him that she cares for him. The two walk into an alley and Jess stands away from a deal. Wall graffiti begins to gel into a shape and reaches out and appears to pull Reggie's arm off. The drug dealers panic and one shoots a gun. The bullet hits Jess in the head and she dies in Reggie's non-mutilated arm.

deck: A member of Art Operatives.
description:
Origin

Not much is known about Krause, but he appears to be a make-up artist that is able to reproduce the appearance of art pieces.

Creation

Written by Shaun Simon and drawn by Mike Allred.

Story Arcs

When the Art Operatives remove the Mona Lisa from her portrait at the Louvre, Krause fixes up the face of a girl that is to act as the stand-in. Later, he is shown at an event honoring the work done by the Art Operatives, but he is clearly relegated to being a man thrust behind the scenes.
